Molthorek the Wizened is a wealthy [[wizard]] living in the [[Laurelbough Ward]] of [[Fairhaven]]. He is widely known for his prophetic prowess, and is said to have predicted the end of the [[Last War]] five years ago to an uncanny degree of accuracy.